    {
      "id": "PopularPost80826",
      "post_content": "@ GrimjawxRULES; [General's Kabuto](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=General's Kabuto) only prevents combat damage, so [Pyroclasm](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pyroclasm) would still kill him. Try [Inviolability](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Inviolability), or better yet, [Indestructibility](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Indestructibility).  \n  \n@tijame: I'm pretty sure this does not stop Annihilator, since Annihilator does not \"target\" you. ",
      "posted_by": "DFG_Danger",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost80826\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">@ GrimjawxRULES; <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=General's Kabuto\">General's Kabuto</a> only prevents combat damage, so <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pyroclasm\">Pyroclasm</a> would still kill him. Try <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Inviolability\">Inviolability</a>, or better yet, <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Indestructibility\">Indestructibility</a>.<br/><br/>@tijame: I'm pretty sure this does not stop Annihilator, since Annihilator does not \"target\" you. </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy838\">DFG_Danger</span>\r\n                                (6/19/2010 3:41:29 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSo